3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper uses deep learning-based solutions for iris recognition. 
4. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is possible as the paper deals with forensic identification. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also possible as the paper explores the differences in feature perception between humans and machines.
